# ── EmailJS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Obtén estos valores en https://dashboard.emailjs.com/
# 1. Service ID  → Email Services → tu servicio conectado a Gmail/Outlook
# 2. Template ID → Email Templates → tu plantilla configurada
# 3. Public Key  → Account → General → Public Key
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=YOUR_SERVICE_ID
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY
